e40891015c0a58843d0","tid":1494843,"uid":143167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cc7e8dcb628139d10cc4f0d2a30790ee897b8e6","tid":1494843,"uid":284716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:30:04.000Z","msg":"好多人都話香港01係紅底、親中<br />\n但係我其實一直都有睇佢啲新聞<br />\n因為佢打嘅caption感覺係幫到我地<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以話俾我知佢究竟係唔係紅底？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pROG9xf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpROG9xf.png&h=df07c857&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrfZbLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrfZbLB.png&h=ba77f5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWghHSi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWghHSi.png&h=155279c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvO745E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvO745E.png&h=e6943e89&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:48:46.000Z","msg":"中國好大，係咁多；蔡東豪都未必係好人，咁立場新聞又睇唔睇先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:37:46.000Z","msg":"立場當然日日睇"},{"pid":"2c954c0642b617f45db2bf25d9ec47330ee52100","tid":1494843,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:52:20.000Z","msg":"上面d人有幾多有認真睇過而唔係睇標題<br />\n咩平時乜乜乜 <br />\n大事大非就點點點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係咁分架</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n睇新聞除左睇標題之外仲可以睇係成間傳媒機構邊一忽寫<br />\n平時新聞/突發係記者寫，睇落去係幾好幾中立<br />\n大事/時事評論係編輯室寫，什致總編輯，口徑（line of speech)當然係係統一左<br />\n<br />\n所以，HK01係佢d評論同埋「編輯室」出個d文先係偏紅"},{"pid":"79ba56212daee16fe1994aea718e65c9d429d714","tid":1494843,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb46f6e8123c509ce10221090b693ab71b4c3ec","tid":1494843,"uid":279401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:58:41.000Z","msg":"老闆係紅色商人于品海<br />\n傳係習派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:53:42.000Z","msg